{"tid":1415592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩和理非/ 淺黃人士用下個腦諗下點解勇武手足會行動升級玩火","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:41.000Z","uid":11254,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f16b09dca1ca20f601e29e3ea96c23f0ced01b","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"而加林鄭條臭西一樣都無回應過呀 <br />\n黑警無法無天 周街開槍<br />\n唔好再講咩失焦 咩對準政權<br />\n而加話事個個係黑警呀 對準黑警係無做錯到架<br />\n不過 勇武手足都要賽後檢討下<br />\n玩火無人會割 但麻煩對準狗屋 <br />\n紀律部隊宿舍唔係全部都係狗住 最好唔好玩火<br />\n同埋如果路上有不同意見人士/影相<br />\n盡量友善小小 唔好下下屌人老母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151219239a724724240f178bb79fce886a854735","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"83e2d7a28df7138dac2e25badeb0a4d57ea6f0e2","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bd9cf833c57a2aede777e332c599aa977e1614f8","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f3572d8f7893645b2cbdf0bc8fdb511716488c45","tid":1415592,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12e9b3f6276dd6ab659a2550c4368669a430a475","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"729b7841136cec2bd0b3cb65c9d2b98efb1a235b","tid":1415592,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"前線做咩都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝義士幫我地出番嘆氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3451e94fa71356f2ac744268ce7c8a9979edfc","tid":1415592,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前線做咩都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝義士幫我地出番啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fef54d9cc4f00128b4bcf6158b1c6e20c234f048","tid":1415592,"uid":70278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"冇人割"},{"pid":"e4701147a205ccf37063cb313801ebcbd6f691b4","tid":1415592,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"面對呢個政府，試著說：核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"5069df6606a0fed7b6d3837af77762f389a43d3d","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ab3093884a4c6f58089c86f04722b3773c1ed7f","tid":1415592,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"我地和理非同勇武已經係命運共同體<br />\n就算我地割左，最尾冇左自由既都係我地<br />\n大家已經番唔到轉頭嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></strong><br />\n自由社會就係每個人都有唔同意見<br />\n勇武派有冇真係傷害過普通市民？有冇針對民居？冇呀<br />\n<br />\n由始至終都係D狗先會亂係民居出彈，射街坊射記者<br />\n佢地而家燒狗屋，唔係對準政權係乜野？<br />\n係呀冇錯佢地有無意中搞到其他紀律部隊，但係都唔夠黑警同黑社會與民為敵咁仆街！！"},{"pid":"ee60aacd3307f4a2bd3447c7c9ac445a8fcaaded","tid":1415592,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>林鄭管治失當+追究警方濫權行為</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n若果當初林鄭 6/9 處理得當<br />\n就唔會發生後續事件<br />\n<br />\n而佢本人亦沒有能力處理今次危機<br />\n林鄭唔配做香港特首<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人唔需要林鄭月娥</span></strong>"},{"pid":"62deb2d1e5779efaab5c9fe8d2a727453e649b30","tid":1415592,"uid":284241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"請前線兄弟姊妹不要玩火和氣油彈，継續和理非一起走"},{"pid":"d73c02022d49383919a845262c93066dc22e42b8","tid":1415592,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"玩火係防線但不是放火煙燻老弱婦孺."},{"pid":"5e1853819d05ca78519f11dee59529c0713ed139","tid":1415592,"uid":103105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港人依家唔需要自詡「和平」同「手無寸鐵」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再望到呢兩個term我比起大家第一時間反感<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我和你老母呀</span></span><br />\n唔洗光環唔洗講到幾清高㗎<br />\n明白目前局勢嘅香港人<br />\n都識講義士放核彈都唔割<br />\n點解呀<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港時代革命」<br />\n「革命不是請客吃飯」<br />\n<br />\n一路行過嚟犠牲咁多同路人<br />\n見盡官警鄉黑勾結幾咁邪惡<br />\n和理非勇武必然雙管齊下去做<br />\n嚟令市民明白背後醜惡<br />\n而且要保持場運動（革命）嘅熱度<br />\n單憑嗌得出「革命」二字<br />\n就知道行動將會無限升級<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">至死方休</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">或者成功</span><br />\n<br />\n但會唔會話因爲勇武要以<strong>極端手段</strong>抗衡邪惡<br />\n就掉轉槍頭屌尻自己人呀<br />\n港豬唔明連登仔都應該明<br />\n<br />\n「一將功成萬骨枯」其實勇武行為背後<br />\n<strong>焦土係必然結果之一</strong><br />\n從古至今要撼動權力核心邊可能唔影響其他人<br />\n犠牲就係咁大，你未準備好可以唔洗嗌革命<br />\n再容許我用「柳暗花明又一村」解釋當下<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">依家係香港最昏最暗嘅時刻</span><br />\n都話只許成功，洗濕咗個頭<br />\n成功過後，仲會有幾多人走去屌勇武？<br />\n<br />\n冇人想話邊個係鬼，前提係互不割蓆。<br />\n未覺醒嘅話，應該都冇咩可以講。<br />\n但唔該唔好再講啲令義士灰心嘅說話。<br />\n唔該大家。</div>"},{"pid":"9b0f2367af238afd1a52488e7ee636ff9eb3ee5e","tid":1415592,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2a8dbf0941d08aab8a122ba772a2d36b57b645b","tid":1415592,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"樓主玩分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾多和理非唔知政府濕鳩<br />\n和理非都有佢地工作要做 唔一定勇武先叫做野<br />\n個口號係兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好理鳩樓主呢d分化撚<br />\n<br />\n我地槍頭要對準"}]}